{"tid":1597314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有無得諗？】民間對話大會","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T02:43:42.000Z","uid":86898,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99bac3a5d1fa628317bfa3a43735d3c444f7133f","tid":1597314,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:37:17.000Z","msg":"同用民間記者會，應對4點鐘狗會發放假訊息如出一轍<br />\n<br />\n林鄭同假黃絲對話<br />\n民間同真藍絲對話<br />\n<br />\n搶返主導權"},{"pid":"9d0a6ea21de52a3659c2c9531e6962474ed1641e","tid":1597314,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:50:10.000Z","msg":"民間對話大會最後會變隻抽大會<br />\n藍絲打人無事 民間比人打會拉哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507ec49ed842539cff49e2fd15d6f4cc96a1d7c1","tid":1597314,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:57:31.000Z","msg":"有得諗<br />\n<br />\n要夾一夾<br />\n<br />\nPush推 <br />\nSignature簽名檔：保衛家園，對抗極權<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對話係陰險策略：請保持不信任<br />\n不割席、不分化、不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n誰也不能代表誰、主權在民<br />\n港人治港、高度自治</strong></span><br />\n條例撒回了，但問題根源還在<br />\n反送中運動轉型為「反極權運動」<br />\n守護香港呢個家，尋求深層次改革<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">行動：Connect 新疆/台灣/中共受害者<br />\n大搞文宣，主線：反極權，撐民主自由<br />\n通過人權與民主法案前，減少暴力畫面<br />\n減輕國際戰線壓力，求加辣/高票數通過<br />\n將「自由對抗極權」傳到世界各地</span><br />\n#antitotalitarianism #anti-chinazi <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>麻煩手足暫時停止升級武力(鏡頭前<br />\n文宣/輿論需要時間追上（國際戰線要人<br />\n(抗爭需要轉型,可持續發展)<br />\n要更多機會比和理非參與<br />\n達至全民一齊追求普世價值</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值/level</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能6.低消費、高儲蓄<br />\n<strong><em>每日任務：</em></strong>1.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶2.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)3.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST4.十點咆哮發泄5.思考完就take action<br />\n<strong><em>每星期任務</em></strong>：1. 罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手4.參加一樣民主活動5. 諗下點樣爭取民主<br />\n<strong><em>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=1badb720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=4dc06f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=63f21e9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.27<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n諗到再加</span>"},{"pid":"a0b3018465ace26694ad0c8b81f24afed3587b49","tid":1597314,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"650d974171be8fc08f39798ff06f234f3cd3c5ad","tid":1597314,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實你呢個已經唔係民間記者會<br />\n而係昇華到全民議政</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實已經係民間議會</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBtw，全力支持<br />\n為你推5下"},{"pid":"caf01155e92d4872b406b463ba2357fa9322a79e","tid":1597314,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92b079e66727e87d8c622709cb13ecf97395bad4","tid":1597314,"uid":62027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64d0846277820113d2ac60817f628a9bfa968546","tid":1597314,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:30.000Z","msg":"民間議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a5df5ee8642921657ae22331129578966f28e1","tid":1597314,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"民間議會x3"},{"pid":"326425b9bd04d259b3e2ae3f5d77101791d4eb8f","tid":1597314,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"民間議會x5"},{"pid":"863d3fd3a6c9312e61905725c4b0fb47cffb4c60","tid":1597314,"uid":266388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q